    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I mean i get the \"both sides\" thing, but u cant really say it's \"complex\" when it feels like so many things labeled as \"woke\" are just people being silenced or called names for having normal opinions. don't you think the censorship aspect is actually becoming the main part of it? like, isn't that a clear negative?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
