      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The rise of \"woke\" discourse has undeniably led to an environment where certain viewpoints are aggressively policed and labeled as unacceptable. This climate of intense social pressure and \"cancellation\" is a clear negative that stifles open debate. When the focus shifts from genuine advocacy to policing language, it functions as a form of ideological censorship. Therefore, the chilling effect on free expression is a significant and undeniable downside of the current trajectory.",
